: [[Willie D. Burton]], [[Michael Herbick]], [[Robert J. Litt]], [[Elliot Tyson]] – [[Die Verurteilten]] ''(The Shawhank Redemption)''
: [[David E. Campbell]], [[Chris David]], [[Douglas Ganton]], [[Paul Massey (Tontechniker)|Paul Massey]] – [[Legenden der Leidenschaft]] ''(Legends of the Fall)''
: [[Michael Herbick]], [[Donald O. Mitchell]], [[Frank A. Montaño]], [[Art Rochester]] – [[Das Kartell]] ''(Clear and Present Danger)''
: [[Tom Johnson (Tontechniker)|Tom Johnson]], [[William B. Kaplan]], [[Dennis S. Sands]], [[Randy Thom]] – [[Forrest Gump]]

=== Bester Tonschnitt ===
